You are that rarest of gems, yales, a passionate anti-nuclear advocate who does not simply retreat to such arguments as &quot;because it's evil&quot; when pressed.  I love it!  Pick at the plan, worry it, hammer on every flaw, please.  Show it to your friends, ask help from professors or activists, beat it down, I dare you!  Heck, who knows, you might even convince me!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
